claim.claim-text:
1. A solid state actuator comprising:
a) a solid state lithium storage material;
b) a solid state volume changing material comprising a metal capable of changing volume in response to lithium insertion and removal;
c) a solid state lithium ion transport material between the lithium storage material and the volume changing material; and
d) a pair of electrodes connected so as to be capable of providing an actuation voltage across the lithium storage material and the volume changing material.

23. An actuator comprising:
a) a storage material;
b) a volume changing material comprising active material structures contained in an ion conducting inactive matrix, the active material structures comprising a material capable of changing volume in response to species insertion and removal;
c) an ion transport material between the storage material and the volume changing material; and
d) a pair of electrodes connected so as to be capable of providing an actuation voltage across the storage material and the volume changing material.
